            },
            {
                "comment": "Paco is a decent professor but I was bothered by the way he made participation mandatory then mocked students for making mistakes on more than one occasion. Attendence is a huge factor in your final grade and many writing assignments are assigned throughout the year. Overall a pretty easy class",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 3
            },
            {
                "comment": "Paco is a great professor in the sense that he only wants his students to improve in their writing. Whether if you're a novice or amateur, he looks for progress in your writing (\"errores b\u00e1sicos) and wants you to pay attention to details. This is overall a great class and nice load to add onto a busy schedule!",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "Paco is a great professor. He always shows up promptly and ready to teach the class. Paco definitely engages everyone and makes the curriculum not as boring as it seems. You can always expect him to constantly give you feedback on your writing and he helps you become a better writer in Spanish.",
